<1ST_LINE>u i AM-Hostages 1stAdd   09-12 0108</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Hostages, 1st Add,0109</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>URGENT</HEAD>
<HEAD>BEIRUT: official said.</HEAD>
<TEXT>
