at Ford's Avon Lake, Ohio, plant outside Cleveland.
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
   Cost: Ford is bearing $1 billion, $900 million of which is to be
invested at the factory.
   Site preparation: To begin by mid-October.
   Plant size: Being expanded from about 1 million square feet to
about 2.2 million square feet.
   Employees: An additional 1,300, bringing total employment to
