minivan.
   Nissan responsibilities: Design and engineering along with
supplying some components.
   Domestic content: Seventy-five percent of the minivan's
components will be made in North America.
   Product marketing: Ford and Nissan will market under separate
nameplates with Ford taking slightly more than half of the
vehicles.
